[{"id":"ab4e4669f4e70380573227b25efb5718","from":"The New York Times","from_email":"nytimes@e.newyorktimesinfo.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"For a Limited Time Digital Subscriptions are Just 99\u00a2.","date":"2014-09-21T10:26:10.000Z","formatted_date":"Sep 21, 2014","formatted_time":"10:26 AM","body":"Try Unlimited Digital.\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\nView in browser:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBUHqGnB81HXJB88ZDoAAwENcmW/viwb?t_params=I_DUSL%3D0%26CAMPAIGN_CODE%3D49XWL%26EMAIL%3Djeeproject%2540yahoo.com%26REGI_ID%3D47275261\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-- THE NEW YORK TIMES -- \n\nTHE WORLD'S FINEST JOURNALISM\n\nJUST 99 CENTS FOR 12 WEEKS ON A DIGITAL SUBSCRIPTION\n\nREDEEM SPECIAL OFFER:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBUHqGnB81HXJB88ZDoAAwENcmW/coresub01\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\nUncompromising integrity. Unrivaled coverage. All with an \nunlimited subscription to NYTimes.com and NYTimes apps; just \n99 cents for your first 12 weeks. Plus, you now get the new \nNYT Opinion app, included free with your subscription, \nbringing you a wide array of the most compelling opinion \npieces anywhere, all in one place, curated by our editors. \nYou'll also get the NYT Now app, featuring news summaries when \nyou're pressed for time and daily briefings to give you a look \nat the day ahead. This offer is for registered users only, \nso subscribe now and never miss a story important to you.\n\nREDEEM SPECIAL OFFER:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBUHqGnB81HXJB88ZDoAAwENcmW/coresub02\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\nFor just 99 Cents for 12 weeks, get unlimited access to:\n\n-- Immersive Storytelling by world-class journalists\n\n-- Best-In-Class Apps such as the new NYT Opinion\n\n-- Innovative